<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | BioBrain</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-bg: #0f172a;
            --accent-teal: #2dd4bf;
            --text-gray: #94a3b8;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #1e293b, var(--primary-bg));
            color: white;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        /* 404 Glitch Effect */
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-teal), #0d9488);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .error-code::after {
            content: "404";
            position: absolute;
            left: 2px;
            top: 2px;
            text-shadow: -2px 0 #ff00c1;
            clip: rect(44px, 450px, 56px, 0);
            animation: glitch 3s infinite linear alternate-reverse;
            background: var(--primary-bg);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: white;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* The Styled Home Button */
        .home-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: var(--accent-teal);
            color: var(--primary-bg);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.3);
        }

        .home-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.4);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        /* Floating Brain/Icon Decoration */
        .bg-decoration {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 15rem;
            opacity: 0.03;
            z-index: -1;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }

        @keyframes glitch {
            0% { clip: rect(10px, 9999px, 85px, 0); }
            20% { clip: rect(80px, 9999px, 10px, 0); }
            40% { clip: rect(30px, 9999px, 50px, 0); }
            60% { clip: rect(15px, 9999px, 90px, 0); }
            80% { clip: rect(60px, 9999px, 20px, 0); }
            100% { clip: rect(5px, 9999px, 95px, 0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <i class="fa-solid fa-brain bg-decoration"></i>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2>Oops! Link Expired or Lost</h2>
        <p>The quiz page you are looking for might have been moved, deleted, or never existed in the BioBrain database.</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="home-btn">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i> Back to Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>